&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About us&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Lucanet is the CFO Solution Platform built for modern finance &amp;amp; tax teams, offering an integrated suite of solutions to simplify and automate their most critical finance processes. More than 6,000 companies around the world rely on our easy-to-use, out-of-the-box SaaS platform - from consolidation and financial planning to tax compliance and reporting, ESG reporting, banking and cash management, and more. PE-backed and growing our footprint across global markets.
&lt;p&gt;Behind the platform is a global team of 850+ people who care about doing the work well. We challenge each other to push boundaries, move fast without cutting corners, and build solutions that genuinely change how finance &amp;amp; tax leaders operate. If you&#39;re looking for a place where your work has real reach - and where your growth is part of the deal - this is it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lucanet.com/en/careers/&quot;&gt;Discover more about Lucanet as an employer.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;TranslationField-module__fieldItem___g4pRX&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Account Manager – Cross-Sell, you will support Lucanet’s growth by identifying and converting new revenue opportunities within our existing customer base. This role is focused on proactive selling; creating demand, engaging new stakeholders, and owning opportunities from first conversation through to close.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work with a high degree of autonomy, using insight, outreach, and commercial curiosity to unlock platform value across accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and qualify cross-sell opportunities within existing customer accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively generate pipeline through outbound outreach, discovery, and internal intelligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage new stakeholders and decision-makers to position Lucanet’s broader platform value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle from initial engagement through to close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Progress opportunities independently with minimal reliance on inbound demand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate CRM data and clear pipeline forecasting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you bring to the table&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong hunter mindset with a bias towards action and outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in an SDR, BDR, or Junior AE role with ambition to own full-cycle deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence creating demand and initiating commercial conversations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage objections and move deals forward with intent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivation driven by ownership, autonomy, and performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Native/Fluent German &amp;amp; English communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
