&lt;li&gt;You will work closely with our sales executives to ensure the company&#39;s goals and targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will work remotely in Germany or in one of our offices hybrid if desired..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
