&lt;li&gt;Assist with notary-related work and coordinate related documentation processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and track statutory filing deadlines and ensure timely, complete, and accurate submissions across jurisdictions.&lt;/li&gt;
