&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an experienced tax professional who can help clients transform their tax function through smart technology, strong process design, and practical tax expertise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Consultant in our Tax Technology team, you will work at the intersection of German tax law, tax processes, and software implementation. You understand how tax departments operate, how regulatory requirements translate into practical processes, and how technology can make tax work more efficient, compliant, and scalable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support companies of different sizes and industries on their journey toward fully digital tax functions. Clients will look to you not only as a tax expert, but also as a trusted advisor who can translate complex tax requirements into clear, practical solutions within our GlobalTaxCenter tax software and related consulting projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with tax specialists, IT experts, product teams, and client stakeholders to shape the ongoing development and implementation of our solutions. If you enjoy combining technical tax knowledge with consulting, problem-solving, and client-facing work, this role offers the opportunity to make a real impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tax Technology &amp;amp; product development Work with tax and IT experts to translate German tax law requirements into functional concepts for our GlobalTaxCenter tax software. You will analyze and objectify tax laws, BMF letters, accounting regulations, and relevant HGB / IFRS requirements so they can be implemented in tax expert systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tax advisory &amp;amp; expert input Bring your income tax and tax process expertise into software development, client discussions, and internal knowledge-building. You will help ensure our solutions remain technically accurate, practical, and aligned with current legal and regulatory developments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementation projects Lead or support challenging client implementation projects, helping tax departments introduce and configure our software in line with their business needs, tax processes, and compliance requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
